               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Maṣḥafa qedar “Book of the Jar” (fols. 3r-34r)
 II) Maṣḥafa taklil
                     “Book of the Marriage Ritual” (fols. 34r-64v)
 - Prayers on the clothes
                     (fols. 34r-41v l.8)
 - Prayers on the bride and the bridegroom (fols. 41v
                     l.8-58r l.12)
 - Order to be read to the bride and the bridegroom (fols.
                     58r l.12-64v)
 
 Colophon.</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">

                     <incipit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </incipit>
                     <explicit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </explicit>
                     <note/>
                     <colophon xml:id="coloph1">
                        <locus target="#64v">64v</locus>
                        <locus target="#12">12</locus>: ዝመጽሐፍ፡ እሞሆይ[sic]፡ ወለተ፡ ኪዳን፡ ዘወሀበቶ፡ ለታቦተ፡ ቅዱሰ፡
                        ሚካኤል፡ ቀርሰበር፡ ከመ፡ ይኩና፡ መርሐ፡ ለመንግሥተ፡ ሰማያት፡ ስመ፡ [<locus target="#65r">65r</locus>]
                        አቡሃ፡ ገብ{ረ}፡ ሐዋርያ፡ ወእማ፡ ወለተ፡ መድኅን፡ ወስመ፡ ውሉዳ፡ ሃይለ፡ ሚካኤል፡ ዐፀደ፡ ማርያም፡ ክንፈ፡ ሚካኤል፡
                        ተጽሕፈ፡ በ፲፻ወ፱፻፸፡ አመተ፡ ምሕረት፡ ዘሠረቆ፡ ውጉዝ፡ ውእቱ፡ በሥልጣነ፡ ጳጳስ፡ አባ፡ ተክለ፡ ሃይማኖት፡ ለጸሐፊሁ፡
                        ገብረ፡ አረጋዊ፡ ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡ አሜን። ወስመ፡ አኃዊሃ፡ ገብረ፡ ትንሣኤ፡ ገብረ፡ ሥላሴ፡ ገብረ፡ ሊባኖስ፡ ሃይለ፡
                        ማርያም፡ ወለተ፡ ሥላሴ፡ ወለተ፡ ሃይማኖት፡ ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡ አሜን። ʾƎmmahoy Walatta Kidān is referred
                        to as the donor of the Ms. Her relatives are also mentioned: her father Gabra
                        Ḥawarya, her mother Walatta Madḫǝn, her sons Haylä Mikāʾel, ʿAḍädä Māryām and
                        Kǝnfa Mikāʾel, and her brothers and sisters. Besides, the colophon mentions the
                        date 1970 A.M. (= 1977/78 A.D.) of the completion of the manuscript, and Takla
                        Hāymānot, the Patriarch of Ethiopia from 1976 to 1988, here called ṗāṗās.
                     </colophon>
                  </msItem>
                  
